values:
everyday brings an unknown hate of me, of you
if i could figure out why rage ruins me i would figure out world peace
only to run brings more pain that comes like a deep wound that blood will ozze out and even when it  stops more is still inder there waiting
oh god if i agree what damage will wait for me?

i think thoughts that manipulate my feelings my mind corupted with heartless beings sharp daggers of mindless indulgence pierce in to the flesh of reality like a child in a fake fantasy punchinh holes in a wall of reality i can not escape this fatality..

i was watching the movie the ***brothers grimm*** and man oh man is that a good movie or what!?! the grim fairy tales writen by the brothers Grimm are brought to life by this movie. A evil queen wanting to live forever with her enchanting beauty is mutalated by an evil plague. WOW and she got the spell to live forever yes but, not to be beautiful as well...she was very beautiful and if she wanted it that bad to try even after death...why not let her have it..if you want something that bad.. here are the brothers..

I was thinking and really thinking and when i watched this movie. My favorite song came on(when the world falls down) when jereth falls in love with sarah and dances with her a a very romantic and lovable ballroom scene and all the while this song in the background was being sung. I really loved the meaning of this love song....read it and see what meaning it holds for you... 1 there is such a sad love, deep in your eyes a kind of pale jewel, open and closed within your eyes i will place the sky within your eyes 2 there is such a fooled heart beating so fast, in search of new dreams a love that will last within your heart i will place the moon within your heart 3 as the pain sweep through makes no sence for you, every thrill has gone was not too much fun at all and i will be there for you when the world falls down.. 4...it is falling.. falling.. falling in love... 5 i will paint you mornings of gold i'll spin you valentine evenings, though we are strangers 'till now we are choosing a path between the stars i willl lay my love between the stars.. repeat of 3 and 4

so as a start i am just going to write about what is on my mind. i am gong to be out of high school VERY VERY soon and i am a little scared as to what i am gong to do with my life. i have plans. to get with my friends after we all graduate and go to japan to train in the arts. that has been one of my main dreams for ever so long. but, so has settling down and being a house wife. i am also so in love right now with my BF Ben. we have been dating for a bout 2 years as a on and off mutual relationship. and we plan to do this japan thing with a few other "close friends". well, they are his friends, i do not like them much but, i will put up with it for now...for now i am to wait and see what will happen...ta ta
